<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figure 6. Cestrum haberii A. K. Monro A Flowering stem B Style C. Longitudinal section through the corolla showing stamen arrangement D Flower. Drawn from W. A. Haber 11049 (MO)." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/9974" pageId="12" pageNumber="61">Fig. 6 A-D</figureCitation>
